andel werden die Gesellschaft neuerlich nachhaltig verändern. "Europa wird nie wieder so sein, wie es einmal war", so beschrieb es André Heller in seinem Künstlergespräch bei der vergangenen GLOBART Academy. Der Historiker Philipp Blom, Trendforscher Harry Gatterer, Bildungsexperte Stephan A. Jansen, die Informatikerin Sarah Spiekermann, Philosophin Lisa Herzog, der Internetexperte Aral Balkan u.v.m. sehen der Wirklichkeit ins Auge und setzen sich mit diesen Veränderungen interdisziplinär auseinander.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aInformation technologyxSocial aspects. 7aART / General.2bisacsh1 aBalkan, Aral, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlom, Philipp, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDobner, Walter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFrischmuth, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGatterer, Harry, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGlobArt, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHerzog, Lisa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJansen, Stephan A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKalkhake, Paulo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKegel, Sandra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLindtner, Silvia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMadary, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMühlenburg, Valerie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPosset, Martin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSpiekermann, Sarah, econtributor.4c